The Fabulous Logic Analyzer #1
==============================

This is a simple logic analyzer software.


System requirements
-------------------

 * Linux
    - Kernel 2.2 or higher
    - libieee1284 installed
    - Qt installed
 * Windows
    - Windows 2000 or XP
 * A parallel port and the schematic attached. The schematic is
   in the source .tar.gz in doc/schematic, in the installed RPM
   it's in /usr/share/doc/packages/tfla-01/.


Installing binaries
-------------------

 * Linux
    - rpm -Uvh tfla-01-<version>.i586.rpm
 * Windows
    - unzip the ZIP file and install on your favourite place, e.g.
      c:\program files.


Building TFLA-01 from source
----------------------------
 
 * Linux
    - export QMAKESPEC=linux-g++
    - adjust PREFIX in tfla-01.pro with your favourite editor
    - qmake tfla-01.pro
    - make
    - lrelease tfla-01.pro
    - make install
 * Windows
    - TODO

